{
  "texts": [
    "In this work, we experimented on benchmarks for Python and Java debugging problems.",
    "Further experimentation is required to discern how well AutoSDwould perform with other languages and benchmarks.",
    "Nonetheless, because the prompt of AutoSDis presented in a zero-shot manner, one would only need to change the debugger examples when the language changes.",
    "Indeed, aside for the Java and Python-specific debugger command examples, our starting prompt did not change when using ARHE and Defects4J.",
    "Finally, the generated explanation may occasionally lend credibility to incorrect patches; by allowing our technique to indicate its confidence in its output and demonstrating that confidence is correlated with correctness, we take the first steps to address this issue."
  ]
}